trans-unit.source: Provides the core implementation for the <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Gir kjerner implementering for den <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: An abstract class, it cannot be instantiated.
trans-unit.target: En abstrakt klasse kan ikke startes.

trans-unit.source: The VirtualFileBase abstract class provides the common methods and properties shared between the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile> and <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den abstrakte klassen VirtualFileBase inneholder vanlige metoder og egenskaper som er delt mellom den <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>og <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory>objekter.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualDirectory> </xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFile>

trans-unit.source: Implementations of these classes provide the ASP.NET runtime with access to files and paths used for compilation.
trans-unit.target: Implementeringer av disse klassene angi kjøretiden ASP.NET med tilgang til filer og baner som brukes for å utføre kompilering.

trans-unit.source: For more information on using virtual files and paths, see the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathProvider> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker virtuelle filer og baner, kan du se <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathProvider>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathProvider>

trans-unit.source: Initializes the class for use by an inherited class instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer klasse for bruk av en arvet klasse-forekomst.

trans-unit.source: This constructor can be called only by an inherited class.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kan bare kalles av en arvet klasse.

trans-unit.source: Although you cannot directly construct an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase> class, you can call this constructor from the constructor of an inheriting class.
trans-unit.target: Selv om du direkte ikke kan opprette en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase>klassen, kan du kalle denne konstruktøren fra konstruktøren for en arvede klasse.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase>

trans-unit.source: Gives a <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"></xref> instance an infinite lifetime by preventing a lease from being created.
trans-unit.target: Angir en <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"> </xref> serverforekomsten uendelig levetid ved å hindre at en leasingavtale som opprettes.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides the <xref:System.MarshalByRefObject.InitializeLifetimeService%2A> method on its base class.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer <xref:System.MarshalByRefObject.InitializeLifetimeService%2A>-metoden på den grunnleggende klasse.</xref:System.MarshalByRefObject.InitializeLifetimeService%2A>

trans-unit.source: It always returns `null` and thereby prevents a lease from being created that would limit the lifetime of the virtual file or directory.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer det alltid `null` og dermed hindrer leasingavtalen opprettes som vil begrense levetiden for virtuelle filen eller mappen.

trans-unit.source: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"></xref> instance represents a virtual file or a virtual directory.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"> </xref> forekomsten representerer en virtuell fil eller en virtuell mappe.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"></xref> instance is a virtual directory; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"></xref> instance is a virtual file.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"> </xref> forekomsten er en virtuell katalogen; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> hvis den <xref href="System.Web.Hosting.VirtualFileBase"> </xref> forekomsten er en virtuell fil.

trans-unit.source: Gets the display name of the virtual resource.
trans-unit.target: Henter visningsnavnet for den virtuelle ressursen.

trans-unit.source: The Name property is typically the file name and extension associated with the resource, although virtual resources may use arbitrary names.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Name er vanligvis filnavn og filtype som er knyttet til ressursen, selv om virtuelle ressurser kan bruke tilfeldig navn.

trans-unit.source: The display name of the virtual file.
trans-unit.target: Visningsnavnet for den virtuelle filen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the virtual file path.
trans-unit.target: Henter den virtuelle filbanen.

trans-unit.source: The VirtualPath property returns the path to the file or directory represented by this object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen VirtualPath returnerer banen til filen eller mappen som er representert av dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: The path to the virtual file.
trans-unit.target: Banen til den virtuelle filen.
